      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it runs and drives smoothly with no known issues, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips or light scratches consistent with normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that is ready for the road immediately.",
