    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable driver that\u2019s ready for the road? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and has plenty of life left in it! While it shows some character through expected wear and tear on the exterior and interior, it remains a dependable choice for anyone seeking value and performance. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a solid car at a very accessible price point!",
