      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in an immaculate, showroom state, reflecting a life of meticulous preservation and climate-controlled storage. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior paint, adheres to the highest standards of excellence. Documented with a comprehensive service history and having undergone a rigorous multi-point certification, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands perfection without compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
